{"aid": "igkq1kjtqki20b", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 3, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6x8l44nF0P", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-28T12:25:07Z", "content": "<p>在20讲 关于消息队列的表述中&#xff0c; 说其是由操作系统维护的以字节序列为基本单位的间接通信机制。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>想知道这个字节序列是怎么传输的&#xff0c; 也是保存在内存中&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": "消息队列的保存位置&#xff1f;"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446636537929, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-05-28T14:33:49Z", "id": "ia8a6zusl535c6", "tag_endorse": [{"class_sections": ["清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "name": "ejacky", "id": "i6x8l44nF0P", "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": false, "us": false}], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-28T14:33:49Z", "content": "<p>消息队列是保存在内存的。它的传输是通过从用户地址空间与内核地址空间的内存复制来完成的。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>下面链接有对消息队列的一个比较完整的介绍&#xff0c;可供参考。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/dyllove98/archive/2009/08/24/2461933.html\">http://www.cnblogs.com/dyllove98/archive/2009/08/24/2461933.html</a></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>如果你有兴趣&#xff0c;可以做一下下面的实验&#xff0c;可观察到消息队列的存储情况。我建议的实验过程是&#xff0c;在两个进程间利用消息队列进行数据通信。第一个进程发消息&#xff0c;全部发送完毕后&#xff0c;进程结束&#xff1b;然后启动第二个进程收消息&#xff0c;观察收到的消息内容和消息总数。修改每个消息的数据量和消息总数&#xff0c;多次做这个实验。有兴趣吗&#xff1f;</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": ["i6x8l44nF0P"], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 46, "created": "2015-05-28T12:25:07Z", "id": "ia85lhhi4nh4gn", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 463, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["q&amp;a"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6x8l44nF0P", "when": "2015-05-28T12:25:07Z", "data": "ia85lhhq9gb4gp", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hdjonbiyfs62ie", "when": "2015-05-28T14:33:49Z", "data": "ia8a6zuxmgu5c7", "to": "ia85lhhi4nh4gn", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["q&amp;a", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": []}}